text":"朋友","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"463d395ffd","type":"paragraph","text":"黑暗的原野已烧起了点点火光","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"429d647a3d","type":"paragraph","text":"静默的天空已响起了阵阵号角","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"24c0d0f1dc","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心一次又一次地激动","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"2cd2a3401b","type":"paragraph","text":"鼓起勇气来吧","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"64eabda5c3","type":"paragraph","text":"鼓起勇气！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"e43b54e8c7","type":"subtitle","text":"让我们鼓起勇气","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"1a81049e5d","type":"paragraph","text":"向一切永恒挑战！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"3d06c41efa","type":"paragraph","text":"凭着我们的勇敢","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"529878b7e8","type":"paragraph","text":"凭着我们的正义","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"f2a812ed7b","type":"paragraph","text":"把恶势力一扫而尽","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"ea72c6360f","type":"paragraph","text":" 以上录自程荣昌1957年1月1日的日记.","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"6f070e9814","type":"paragraph","text":"5月19日又写道：“趁上政治经济学时间，草了一稿。我仿流沙河的‘草木篇’形式而写的，表示我对‘草木篇’的赞同。我用的题目是‘兽禽篇’，决定交给你们，看他们是否给我登出来。”“兽禽篇”后来登在云大“三好”墙报上，原文如下：","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"f7a1b26f32","type":"subtitle","text":"兽禽篇","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"ea73a2a2f1","type":"paragraph","text":"两足而羽谓之禽，四足而毛谓之兽，——尔雅。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"3da385d6af","type":"paragraph","text":"人之为人者，非禽兽也。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"55f2343fa3","type":"subtitle","text":"白兔","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"e6afaa99d3","type":"paragraph","text":"多么温柔的性情，从来也没有一点儿脾气，他的特征是：顺从，顺从……一个小狗可以追他一趟，这虽然使他气喘，但是他，沉默。一支公鸡也要向他挑战，他虽然有些不满，但是他，沉默。最后，主人把他绑在解剖台上，临终了，他仍然是沉默。主人说，你的修养很好。野兔说，兄弟，你太软弱了。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"d406d46fe5","type":"subtitle","text":"鹦哥","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"16c6f41bdf","type":"paragraph","text":"她，羽毛诱人，能说会道。站在客人来往的路旁，她从来不识对象，逢来了一个衣冠整齐的人，她的经过训练的喉就会叫出：客人来了！客人来了！欢迎、欢迎。声音宛转，情意深长，好心的客人，往往赔她一个微笑，主人也很满意，她的善于接待，但是，却不知道她还别有用意。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"0bbd98abad","type":"subtitle","text":"狗熊","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"20983723e5","type":"paragraph","text":"一见就知，他的形态长得有些夸张，一举一动，都有点逗人发笑，他整天忙碌，似乎想有所作为，其实，那只是他的本能和装饰，他曾说现在还有谁配做我的朋友，的确是这样。如果与兔做朋友，那么他就没有欺侮的了，因为朋友间是不能互相欺侮的。如果与象做朋友呢？他又不愿，因为象的力量比他大。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"d4e66390b3","type":"appellation","text":"矢咕咕","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"e8d84f3d94","type":"paragraph","text":"不知他的学名，昆明人都叫他矢咕咕，造物主在他的头顶上，装饰了一束长羽毛，他的尾巴，也长得花骚，声音又那么优怨，人们一定会认为他是凤凰的同族，或者就是凤凰的同胞。他就因人们这种错觉，而神气了起来，其实了解矢咕咕的人都知道，他最高兴的是最肮脏的地方，只要一与他接近一般恶心的臭气便会冲进你的鼻腔。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"f44e0ad332","type":"subtitle","text":"老鼠","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"5e156de338","type":"paragraph","text":"人言“胆小如鼠”，其实，老鼠的胆子并不小，只要睡了后，最贵重的东西，他也敢破坏，只是他们不愿在白天出来，而选择夜间活动，因为夜对他们来说是安全的。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"72de7dc844","type":"appellation","text":"人又言，“猫猫不在家，老鼠打翻家”，可是猫对老鼠说来是有威信的，但是，并非绝对，在没有猫的场合下，老鼠就要大显身手了。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"f53c3a911d","type":"paragraph","text":"在反击右派以后，程荣昌又在他1957年6月24日的日记中写道：","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"2f050fc82a","type":"paragraph","text":"两天来都是对“春雷”上的文章进行批判，谈论内容也是：思想动机哪、根源哪、立场哪、阶级出身哪等。这些都是老一套了，看来也再不会有什么更好的法宝了。但是所有这些都是建立在一个基础上的。没有这个基础，人们就不会怕这一套了。这个基础就是他们利用了人们的贪生、享乐思想。贪生、享乐这东西倒没有什么值得非议的，因为这是人的一种本能。但是“生”有两种：一种是光明磊落的生，一种是暗淡无光的生。被人利用的是后一种生，光明磊落的生是不会被人利用的。“乐”也有两种：一种是共同的乐，这种乐是中间传统思想上的“……后来下之乐而乐”的乐；另一种是狭隘的乐，被人利用的也是后一种乐。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"fca247dc53","type":"paragraph","text":"“批判”这没有什么，使我气愤的是语文被恶魔利用了，他们用语言去做一切坏事。趁“批判”时间写下面的两首诗：","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"58056b0262","type":"subtitle","text":"其一","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"c427dcb7e0","type":"paragraph","text":"不听吗？不行","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"2a6d9f6de0","type":"paragraph","text":"语言","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"fdd046ccfb","type":"paragraph","text":"真不幸","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"0191fa6005","type":"paragraph","text":"你成了罪恶者的工具","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"bbcb62b13c","type":"paragraph","text":"他们利用你去献媚讨好","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"11cc4be85f","type":"paragraph","text":"利用你去掩盖一切卑鄙龌龊","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"0806a3f253","type":"paragraph","text":"利用你去散布毒汁","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"1168b018a9","type":"paragraph","text":"正直被丑化了","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"67d61d5f25","type":"paragraph","text":"丑恶却被点缀得花花绿绿","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"2c6f88497b","type":"paragraph","text":"正常的人往往是神经失常","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"dfe14d09e8","type":"subtitle","text":"其二","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"e6cff2439b","type":"paragraph","text":"朋友  当你端起人生的酒杯","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"d9403c2257","type":"paragraph","text":"喝下第一口时","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"a9dac41b67","type":"paragraph","text":"如果  你不感到是苦的","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"2d87f7b97c","type":"paragraph","text":"那末你也是一个虚伪者","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"74be352280","type":"paragraph","text":"人生的酒杯已经不亮了","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"5c2affb6a0","type":"paragraph","text":"它已被魔爪所污染","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"736c61f746","type":"paragraph","text":"人生的酒已经不甜了","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"61eab0e9bc","type":"paragraph","text":"魔鬼已在液中下了毒","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"02a0ed4384","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的人","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"a8a9d4ee62","type":"paragraph","text":"就不能拒绝端起人生的酒杯","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"c574ebf251","type":"paragraph","text":"酒虽苦","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"d539dbb17a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们也得喝","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"c73b795b7b","type":"paragraph","text":"为了我们的未来","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"9e4887211f","type":"paragraph","text":"为了我们的子孙","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"541de34fb8","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要下定决心","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"6a51d73bc7","type":"paragraph","text":"把人生的酒杯重新洗净","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"8a49cda699","type":"paragraph","text":"要健全我们的胃肠","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"cef7e4d830","type":"paragraph","text":"将一切有互不的苦酒喝尽","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"6c95ab42c3","type":"paragraph","text":"程荣昌还说:","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"d833c9aeb3","type":"paragraph","text":"在中国是“党天下”","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"e8a27b6622","type":"paragraph","text":"现在中国是“党天下”，民主党派没地位。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"994cb413f5","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联侵略匈牙利","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"c460253965","type":"paragraph","text":"匈牙利事件，苏联两次出兵是侵略。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"45572b0332","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联不将帝俄所占去的黑龙江一带归还就是不友好。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"a80d675ff7","type":"subtitle","text":"中国援助朝、越是打肿脸充胖子","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"},{"id":"b47835e0c8","type":"paragraph","text":"美国侵略朝鲜不是为了侵略中国，为什么中国要出兵？中国对越南、朝鲜援助，是打肿了脸充胖子。我国很穷，猪肉不够吃，农民生活根本没有改善，不应该援助邻邦国家。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9"}],"page":{"id":"b3a4d994c8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"29dc63f0c9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}